OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782740880
OL,3,CConservatives name candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,FThe Conservative Party has announced
OL,7,FTrafford councillor Phil Eckersley as
OL,8,Fits candidate in the by-election for
OL,9,Fthe Greater Manchester mayoralty
OL,10,Ftriggered by Andy Burnham's election
OL,11,Fas an MP.
OL,13,FMr Eckersley currently represents
OL,14,FBowdon Ward on Trafford Council, where
OL,15,Fhe serves as deputy leader of the
OL,16,FTrafford Conservative Group.
OL,18,FHe previously served as president of
OL,19,Fthe Greater Manchester Chamber of
OL,20,FCommerce Wigan division.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
