CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782740880
OL,3,CConservatives name candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,FThe Tory candidate is also a local
OL,7,Fbusinessman who founded Bridgewater
OL,8,FHome Care in 2010 in Wigan and has
OL,9,F"grown it into a successful care
OL,10,Fbusiness supporting vulnerable and
OL,11,Folder people across the region, while
OL,12,Femploying more than 100 staff," the
OL,13,Fparty said.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
