PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782740880
OL,3,CConservatives name candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,FHe said: "I am honoured to have been
OL,7,Fselected as the Conservative candidate
OL,8,Ffor mayor of Greater Manchester.
OL,9,FGreater Manchester is my home, and
OL,10,Fit's a region with enormous potential,
OL,11,Fbut too often decisions are made with
OL,12,Fa focus on Manchester City Centre `
OL,13,Fwith the outer boroughs getting left
OL,14,Fbehind.
OL,16,F"As a business owner, father and local
OL,17,Fcouncillor, I understand the
OL,18,Fchallenges facing families, businesses
OL,19,Fand communities across our city region.
OL,26,@nD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
