PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782740880
OL,3,CConservatives name candidate to
OL,4,Creplace Burnham as Manchester mayor
OL,6,F"From pressure on public services and
OL,7,Fconcerns about crime and antisocial
OL,8,Fbehaviour, to congestion, housing and
OL,9,Fthe need for stronger local economies,
OL,10,Fthese are issues I have dealt with
OL,11,Fdirectly throughout my professional
OL,12,Fand public life.
OL,14,F"The Conservative Party has a clear
OL,15,Fvision for Greater Manchester, safer
OL,16,Fstreets, better transport, thriving
OL,17,Flocal businesses, responsible
OL,18,Fdevelopment and value for taxpayers'
OL,19,Fmoney."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@GO]
